 1 — Python borligini tekshiring

  python3 --version
  Yo'q bo'lsa:
  sudo apt install python3 python3-pip python3-venv -y

  ---
  2 — Agent fayllarini ko'chiring

  Birinchi noutbukda terminal oching:
  scp -r /home/dior/Desktop/SIEM/my-siem/agent boshqa_noutbuk_IP:/home/USERNAME/siem-agent

  Yoki GitHub dan yuklab oling (ikkinchi noutbukda):
  git clone https://github.com/DiorDevv/SIEM.git
  cd SIEM/agent

  ---
  3 — Virtual environment va paketlar

  cd ~/SIEM/agent
  python3 -m venv venv
  source venv/bin/activate
  pip install -r requirements.txt

  ---
  4 — Config sozlang

  nano config.yaml
  O'zgartiring:
  manager_url: http://84.8.147.84:8080
  agent_name: ikkinchi-noutbuk

  ---
  5 — Systemd service yarating

  sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/siem-agent.service

  Yozing (USERNAME ni o'zgartiping):
  [Unit]
  Description=SIEM Agent
  After=network.target

  [Service]
  Type=simple
  User=USERNAME
  WorkingDirectory=/home/USERNAME/SIEM/agent
  ExecStart=/home/USERNAME/SIEM/agent/venv/bin/python3 agent.py
  Restart=always
  RestartSec=10

  [Install]
  WantedBy=multi-user.target

  ---
  6 — Ishga tushiring

  sudo systemctl daemon-reload
  sudo systemctl enable siem-agent
  sudo systemctl start siem-agent
  sudo systemctl status siem-agent

  ---
  SIEM dashboardda yangi agent ko'rinadi. Savolingiz bo'lsa ayting!
